# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Symlinked config protection
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Since /home/anand/anand-dots/configs is symlinked to
# ~/.config, changes to live system configs may reflect
# in this repo. Use .gitignore to prevent committing
# personal/system-specific modifications.

# Runtime/generated files (never commit):
configs/hypr/current_wallpaper
configs/rofi/wallpaper.rasi

# Waypaper: personal state (modified by GUI, not defaults)
# Uncomment if waypaper config changes shouldn't be tracked:
# configs/waypaper/

# System-specific personal modifications:
# Add patterns below to ignore personal overrides:
# configs/waybar/custom.conf
# configs/kitty/custom.conf

# Always exclude backups/test files:
*.bak
*.test
*.swp
